T1  - Linking prefunding factors and high-technology venture success: An exploratory study
AU  - Roure, Juan B.
AU  - Maidique, Modesto A.
JO  - Journal of Business Venturing
VL  - 1
IS  - 3
SP  - 295
EP  - 306
PY  - 1986
DA  - 1986/09/01/
